mp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3254623/sooner-or-later-stakes-are-high-chinese-summit-japan-and-south-korea-not-urgent?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国和俄罗斯对国际规则态度不同的十大原因</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254514/10-reasons-china-and-russia-differ-their-approach-international-rules?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着多极化成为趋势，有必要比较新兴国家之间以及新兴国家与西方国家之间的差异。俄罗斯和中国有着密切的战略伙伴关系，但在世界舞台上的观点和行为却截然不同。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 11:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/asia/article/3254514/10-reasons-china-and-russia-differ-their-approach-international-rules?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>瑞典爱立信否认退出中国市场，尽管面临来自华为的5G设备竞争和地缘政治紧张局势</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255210/swedens-ericsson-denies-exiting-china-market-despite-5g-equipment-competition-huawei-geopolitical?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该公司在最新的财务报告中指出，中瑞关系的不确定性是主要的业务风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 10:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3255210/swedens-ericsson-denies-exiting-china-market-despite-5g-equipment-competition-huawei-geopolitical?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>世界上第一个人工智能开发的治疗致命肺部疾病的药物在中国和美国进入具有里程碑意义的临床试验</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3255232/worlds-first-ai-developed-drug-deadly-lung-disease-enters-landmark-clinical-trials-china-us?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>研究人员表示，人工智能工具可以将早期分析时间缩短数年的证据将“彻底改变药物发现”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3255232/worlds-first-ai-developed-drug-deadly-lung-disease-enters-landmark-clinical-trials-china-us?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国5%的GDP目标未能让亚洲放心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3255100/why-chinas-5-cent-gdp-target-has-failed-reassure-asia?utm_source=rss_feed</link><des